title: Permanent Toolbar
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

The permanent toolbar stays on the top of the page, even as you scroll through the page vertically. It displays a hamburger menu to toggle the drawer, and the $:/SiteTitle tiddler followed by the [[$:/SiteSubtitle]] tiddler as a heading.